**/notes.md

# pcap captures (often big, sometimes contain secrets)
*.pcap
*.pcapng
**/captures/*

# Terraform
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
crash.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# Secrets / keys
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
!**/tls-lab/**/*.crt
!**/tls-lab/**/*.key
*.priv
.env
.env.*

# Editor
.DS_Store
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/
node_modules/

# kind/k3d
kubeconfig
kubeconfig-*

# Wireshark
*.pcap.gz

# Keep .gitkeep
!.gitkeep
